<br>
Yes, if you are wielding a 2h weapon and wish to revert to 2-1h weapons, it works just like the shield..click on the right hand weapon and the left is auto equipped.<br>
<br>
As far as the others go..I didnt go for the shadowzerker, but rather the shadowslinker.  at 24 I have 24 crit strike, 20 stealth, some in axe and 10 envenom.  I have found that in RvR, I am pretty much unseen and can 1 shot casters easily and 2 hits for infis, friars and most scouts.  This is using a 2h axe.  I don't know how well the left axe styles are, but I seem to hold my own against 1 (and most times 2) with just crit styles.  Perf Artory is ruthless and followed by garrote and anything else I can rummage up makes Hauntin pretty mean.  I don't know if I&quot;d be willing to be completely unseen by a same lvl infi and getting a good PA on him for the ability to use some lower level left axe styles.<br>
<br>
I need to play Haunt a little more to give you better info..I havent really done RvR and switched from 2h to 2-1h simply because I do so much damage..no need to interrupt any casters since they're dead in 1 hit, but I do need to see how fast a couple of 1handers can whittle up on a few tanks or friars..<br>
<br>
